Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:13.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:59.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:14.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:18.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.77,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(427.167,140.389)}The Sea Snake Man of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.77,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(527.167,690.389)}the Ghost Village
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a strange sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, weird...\N- Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!\NAre you trying to get killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Let me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell I will, jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you take me somewhere\NI can get a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a criminal on the\Nrun, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... a resident employee\Nof Okuyama Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A policeman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been through the most awful things...\Nyou'd never believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys wouldn't believe\Nme if I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our village just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I need a phone, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a rest stop\Njust beyond that tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use the phone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...\Nthere should be a rest stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We just passed this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right... no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to turn us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe to back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:23.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man's beams give him the\Npower to change the scenery around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we made it\Nthrough, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- He melted!\N- He's melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You will now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive... keep driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.56,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H000000&\3c&H40CDB8&\fad(0,500}Tokyo {\fs70\c&H05008E&\bord0}<—> {\fs60\c&H000000&\3c&H40CDB8&\bord3.6}Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody driving it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going on?\N- That's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one inside...\Nno driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much too early\Nfor all this fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even read my newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all Goro's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro's a lazybones anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should wake up earlier and help\Nme, or make breakfast some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a reason I\Nslept in this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I last\Nsaw Pops in such a temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro...\Nare you making mischief again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing my homework last night,\Nand I heard this late night news report...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't listen to the\Nradio while doing homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There was this weird sound\Nthat came over the broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it turned into\Nthese nonsense words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, what were the words?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... "Ka-tsu-yo-shi."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It kept repeating,\Nso I got curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, don't you realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuyoshi... Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ka-tsu-yo-shi...\NShi-yo-tsu-ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Goro was hearing...\Na Shocker message?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of\Ndirective, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.\NI saw the strangest article...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker could be behind it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Story of the Ghost Truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It raced down Route 246 at\Nfull speed with no driver."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,246?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki went out in that\Ndirection this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to help with the\Nplans for a new motocross course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki took a helicopter to scope out\Nthe proposed site for courses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountains, valleys, flatlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This will make a great course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Villagers, in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The sight of a helicopter shouldn't\Nbe that surprising to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:07.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man has been equipped with\Nthis Shocker invention, the prism eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It lets the beams he emits\Ndeceive the human eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,making them think the\Nscenery has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:17.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker intends to use this device to\Nspread mass panic all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell,\NTaki has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, the perpetual thorn\Nin Shocker's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a moth flying\Nright into a flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Show that young man\Nwhat you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's taken\Nover the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker... where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourselves, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is a Shocker\Ncyborg training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, behold my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never\Nescape this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the helicopter\Nthat flew towards Okuyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have to be\Nout of fuel by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it crashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get any\Nreports about a crash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing like that, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of an engine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uninhabited!\NThere's no pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- It can't be!\N- It's flying itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get around behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No fuel, no pilot,\Nbut it still landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure of the flight plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He was set to take aerial\Nphotos around Okuyama Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Taki? Talk, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the power I've mastered\Nin the Shocker training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man... tell me the\Nlocation of Shocker's training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It would do you no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you will die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the power of\Nthe training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:27.93,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I follow him back,\NI can find the Shocker training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be that village...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Taki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki must have landed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki...\N- I made it through, more or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, Shocker has\Ntaken over the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're using it as\Na training ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent people are being killed\Nevery day by Sea Snake Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, why haven't you escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker sees everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you get\Nhere, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I played possum and\Nthen followed him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...\Nhelp these people, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone,\Nwe're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on,\Nwe're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's get out of\Nhere, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!\N- Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold tight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!\N- Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone hold hands\Nand stay close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...\Nwe just can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing\Nthat always happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki,\Ncan you handle things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a device\Ncausing hallucinations...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see if I can\Nfind a way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They have power over\Nthis area somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Sea Snake Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When his eyes reflect sunlight,\Nhe generates illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:11.23,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi,\Nyou cannot escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell,\Nwhat are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the true purpose\Nof the training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd reveal\Nour secrets to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man... finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Snake Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you use that device\Nto create those illusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant as ever,\NHongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You deduced the secret\Nof the prism eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Sea Snake Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it's time for\Nthe final battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Back Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally defeated\NSea Snake Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.77,0:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was your strength to\Nkeep going through your fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that drove the villain away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, show us those smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, you okay?\N- Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:55.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The power of the Kamen Rider\Nin defeating Sea Snake Man
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:58.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,restored peace to\Nthe "ghost village."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:02.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would continue to concoct\Ntheir dreadful plans in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:05.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight for justice and peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:10.51,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.39,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:15.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:16.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Cockroach Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:20.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His terrible white powder\Ncauses humans to age to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:23.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's insatiable desire\Nfor world domination continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:24.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:26.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:30.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Cockroach Man!!\NThe Dreadful Germ-Stuffed Ad Balloon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs123\bord.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}Cockroach Man!! The Dreadful\N Germ-Stuffed Ad Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:40.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:43.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:45.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:48.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:54.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:03.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:07.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:10.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Snake Man of\Nthe Ghost Village
Comment: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back and add TL NOTE